portable to) any system that supports OpenGL 1.4 with ARB shaders, SDL and OpenAL. Compared to the original version of Doom 3, Dhewm 3 has many bugfixes, supports EAX-like sound effects on all operating systems and hardware (via OpenAL Softs EFX support), has much better support for widescreen resolutions and has 64bit support. It only supports old Mods if they either don&apos;t require their own game DLL or have been ported to Dhewm 3 - see the Mods page for more information. Mod-binaries who are supported, are bundled with Dhewm 3. External data is still required. Note that while the Doom 3 source code has been released under GPL, you still need to legally own the game and provide Dhewm 3 the game data to play. See the How to Install section for more informationgversionh1.5.5preldownload_urlxphttps://github.com/tx00100xt/dhewm3-appimage/releases/download/1.5.5pre/Dhewm3-20250209-1.5.5pre-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh40.77 MBhsrc_urlsĀx5https://github.com/tx00100xt/dhewm3-appimage/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/tx00100xtglicenseĀgGPL-3.0kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package¨cpkgpdiffuse.appimagehpkg_namegdiffusefpkg_idx$appimage.github.io.Diffuse.icidassetkdescriptionx?A music player which connects to your cloud/distributed storagegversione3.5.0ldownload_urlxYhttps://github.com/icidasset/diffuse/releases/download/3.5.0/diffuse_3.5.0_amd64.AppImagedsizei165.94 MBhsrc_urlsĀx-https://github.com/icidasset/diffuse/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/icidassetglicenseĀcMITkmaintainersx9AppImage (ht