ing. There are no fixed class restrictions, so you can develop your character in any way you wish. You, as a player, determine exactly how you develop your character. If you make mistakes, or decide to change or adjust your build, you can do so. Eternal Lands is not just about combat. Many players focus on more peaceful activities such as collecting resources, creating items, summoning monsters and so on. But if you like combat, there is plenty of it as well, both PvP and PvE. Eternal Lands is owned and run by Radu Privantu. This package is built and maintained by one of the client developers known in game as bluapgversioni1.9.7.0-4ldownload_urlxohttps://github.com/raduprv/Eternal-Lands/releases/download/1.9.7.0-4/EternalLands-Linux-x86_64_1.9.7.0.AppImagedsizei209.75 MBhsrc_urlsĀx1https://github.com/raduprv/Eternal-Lands/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/raduprvglicenseĀgQPL-1.0kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package¨cpkgxeternalmodmanager.appimagehpkg_nameqeternalmodmanagerfpkg_idx1appimage.github.io.EternalModManager.PowerBall253kdescriptionxtA cross platform mod manager for DOOM Eternal, making it easier to set-up and install mods in both Windows and Linuxgversionfv4.2.1ldownload_urlxnhttps://github.com/brunoanc/EternalModManager/releases/download/v4.2.1/EternalModManager-4.2.1-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh39.61 MBhsrc_urlsĀxChttps://github.com/PowerBall253/EternalModManager-Avalonia/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/PowerBall253glicenseĀcMITkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImag