most all IR protocols known to the Internet community can be generatedgversionhci-buildldownload_urlxxhttps://github.com/bengtmartensson/IrScrutinizer/releases/download/ci-build/IrScrutinizer-2.4.3-SNAPSHOT-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh39.21 MBhsrc_urlsĀx=https://github.com/bengtmartensson/harctoolboxbundle/releaseshweb_urlsĀx"https://github.com/bengtmartenssonglicenseĀgGPL-3.0kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package¨cpkgpisolate.appimagehpkg_namegisolatefpkg_idx%appimage.github.io.Isolate.seenaburnskdescriptionxLightweight image browsergversionfv2.0.2ldownload_urlx\https://github.com/seenaburns/isolate/releases/download/v2.0.2/isolate-2.0.2-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh48.50 MBhsrc_urlsĀx.https://github.com/seenaburns/isolate/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/seenaburnsglicenseĀkNOASSERTIONkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package¨cpkgrjreleaser.appimagehpkg_nameijreleaserfpkg_idx&appimage.github.io.JReleaser.jreleaserkdescriptionyļJReleaser is a release automation tool. Its goal is to simplify creating releases and publishing artifacts to m