) as well as with a graphical user interface (GUI). It also supports operation as a CGI program for a web server to provide PDF-formatted output from a web page. The GUI starts automatically if you run HTMLDOC without any options. Since support for Markdown input and EPUB output is still under development, both options are not available from the GUI, but only from the CLIgversionjcontinuousldownload_urlxźhttps://github.com/pdfkungfoo/htmldoc/releases/download/continuous/htmldoc-v1.9.3-travisbuild.26-travisbranch.master-git.4ab539d-x86_64.AppImagedsizeg4.57 MBhsrc_urlsĀx/https://github.com/KurtPfeifle/htmldoc/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/KurtPfeifleglicenseĀeGPL-2kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package¨cpkgnhugin.appimagehpkg_nameehuginfpkg_idx%appimage.github.io.hugin.aferrero2707kdescriptionx‚An easy to use cross-platform panoramic imaging toolchain based on Panorama Tools. With Hugin you can assemble a mosaic of photographs into a complete immersive panorama, stitch any series of overlapping pictures and much moregversionjcontinuousldownload_urlxąhttps://github.com/aferrero2707/hugin-appimage/releases/download/continuous/Hugin_Panorama_Creator-2019.0.beta1-20190126-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh45.66 MBhsrc_urlsĀx7https://github.com/aferrero2707/hugin-appimage/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/aferrero2707glicenseĀgGPL-2.0kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarant