ager extended with some useful ideas from mutt. If you use Vim, Vifm gives you complete keyboard control over your files without having to learn a new set of commands. It goes not just about Vim like keybindings, but also about modes, options, registers, commands and other things you might already like in Vim. Just like Vim, Vifm tries to adhere to the Unix philosophy. So instead of working solutions which are set in stone user is provided with a set of means for customization of Vifm to one&apos;s likings. Though builtin functionality should be enough for most of use casesgversiongv0.14.3ldownload_urlxShttps://github.com/vifm/vifm/releases/download/v0.14.3/vifm-v0.14.3-x86_64.AppImagedsizeg1.79 MBhsrc_urlsĀx%https://github.com/vifm/vifm/releaseshweb_urlsĀwhttps://github.com/vifmglicenseĀpGPL-2.0-or-laterkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package¨cpkgrvioletbug.appimagehpkg_nameivioletbugfpkg_idx%appimage.github.io.violetbug.belltownkdescriptionx2A cross-platform Roku Debugger graphical interfacegversionfv0.0.5ldownload_urlx^https://github.com/belltown/violetbug/releases/download/v0.0.5/violetbug-0.0.5-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh48.44 MBhsrc_urlsĀx.https://github.com/belltown/violetbug/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/belltownglicenseĀkMIT Licensekmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inac